{"tid":1093661,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【暗笑陳奕迅黑面事件】鄭中基去大學分享：今日無見人玩手機 呢啲咪做出水準來","createTime":"2019-04-05T18:07:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T05:20:45.000Z","uid":130626,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ca0df9409ea02e06e9dedd050cd527d971a46e43","tid":1093661,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T18:07:16.000Z","msg":"早排陳奕迅喺一間公開大學演講時，因為唔like啲學生只掛住同佢合照，同埋玩手機，攪到黑晒面，仲叫一啲學生離場。近日「暴龍哥」鄭中基亦都去大學做分享，班港大學生見到暴龍哥出現，個個十足牛歡喜一樣，勁high呀！ <br />\n對住班學生，鄭中基都忍唔住暗笑陳奕迅。「起碼今日無見到人玩電話先，呢啲咪叫做做出水準來！就算有，佢哋攞嚟影相啫！」<br />\n幽默呢個主題，開正佢個瓣，所以一個鐘頭嘅分享，真係笑聲笑聲，滿載溫馨呀！<br />\n之前暗笑Eason，跟手同啲學生玩美女廚房，Ronald笑埋佢舊拍檔方力申，仲有古天樂。不過喺呢位搞笑高手眼中，最識講笑嗰個，竟然係成日板起塊面嘅劉青雲。佢亦過兩招畀學生，幽默呢家嘢，就好似投資一樣，事前要學識風險評估，否則會如昔日嘅佢，好易賴嘢，得罪人。<br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_662727_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_662727_0&d=K4UaoR%2Bzp7qM8XPwf0LBI7M5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=cdc45085\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_662727_0&h=976007c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_662727_0</a>"},{"pid":"4853cece678e0caf83103e118b0c3ef7f4decdf8","tid":1093661,"uid":43061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T18:09:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />句句有骨WO"},{"pid":"8921d6f2b62914b986d2e37f19d1caf090ff6779","tid":1093661,"uid":242009,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T18:30:24.000Z","msg":"抽到應一應喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n單丸會唔會嬲豬架"},{"pid":"7ee0b789b9433b672e23dc4aa14d67923e532808","tid":1093661,"uid":155732,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T18:31:41.000Z","msg":"港大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nOU垃圾點同精英比<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e6d393e0d